{"tid":1716762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇人阻到我做物資仔","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:44:14.000Z","uid":221360,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6abad82d49b76a7fcdbd094815ef933f53c331f1","tid":1716762,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"話說今日有個傻仔，因為尋晚發完夢返屋企睇live睇到中大學生比黑驚攻打，睇到喊晒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以決定第二日罷工朝早就去中大送物資。<br />\n點知佢住果到乜車都出唔到去，佢靈機一捉決定行山上大圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...唔係講笑d斜路多到呢，佢又十年冇做運動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/voc8RZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvoc8RZY.png&h=ce9c2a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zmoggrM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzmoggrM.png&h=257b3c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtbUNyA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtbUNyA.png&h=352484a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾經辛苦終於到左大圍，之後去左執笠倉買物資啦。哇...你班友仔好似d貨唔洗錢咁乜都比你地清晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我唯有買幾個尿袋入去啦...點知搵唔到單車，要行到沙田先搵到一架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦乜都齊晒就出發啦，沿路見到好多步兵拎住一袋二袋入緊去，果種心情...好耐都未試過咁開心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聞住馬屎味終於到左中大孖橋，點知佢同我講d物資full晒，唔會再收，淨係收火魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他拎返走...咁果幾個尿袋唯有等下次。之後就繼續無限loop買啤酒，到左5點左右終於完成任務...都唔記得左自己晒左幾支酒。<br />\n點解會有咁傻既人...冇錯果個就係我喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然好辛苦，但都覺得值得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家去緊其他區睇有咩幫手，順便休息下發下post。<br />\n<br />\n各位我唔係想講自己有做d咩，我只係想講...我都係社會人，我都有屋企人要養，我都係一個普通熱愛香港呢個家既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由6月開始，我都係維持住做和理非...但呢個月發生既事，我真係過唔到自己果關，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望自己屋企人體諒我。<br />\n<br />\n今日仲繼續返工或者仲係屋企睇live既人，你地對得住自己良心咩？<br />\n<br />\n藍黃是政見 黑白是良知。<br />\n藍黃野我而家唔會點批評，之前係連登都因為自己失晒理智亂覆野，係到講返聲sor9ly先。大家理念唔同就唔同，一定有爭拗。但黑白唔同，黑就黑白就白，冇良知就唔應該。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，醒喇好嘛？</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n不自由 毋寧死</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6f87ddf9d01d5790f8ad224eeffc10f04a04ad26","tid":1716762,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"f7cb134d981bcd51080d7c448083d93eea54ca16","tid":1716762,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"dc3ed5627148c2618c645d755eecc232ddbfea7d","tid":1716762,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"c1726ef1793af3d6082ac20ea2b69689dadc2cee","tid":1716762,"uid":295981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦哂"},{"pid":"d2676244b6dddc8a70b2e08e36b81792ef100116","tid":1716762,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"aeede563721db8e86704343a56e8cd675c64518e","tid":1716762,"uid":224857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"勁，不過揚左位"},{"pid":"3f9582d372b72a5ff899350b4e135c9dc58eeb56","tid":1716762,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"41416d8b5f26933209ff7feded5716188c79f254","tid":1716762,"uid"